The paper deals with image processing and recognition, specifically in the field of plant identification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of color moments and vein features also suggests a possible fit with cs.MM (Multimedia), while the use of machine learning algorithms such as PNN and SVM suggests a possible fit with cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the use of a dataset for experimentation suggests a possible fit with cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
